.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Python/Jupyter cache
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Local environments and secrets
.env
.env.*
.venv/
venv/
env/
.conda/

# Logs and temporary files
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak

# Keep folder docs, ignore heavy or licensed datasets by default.
data/raw/*
!data/raw/README.md
data/interim/*
!data/interim/README.md
data/processed/*
!data/processed/README.md
data/external/*
!data/external/README.md

# Notebook-local input/output folders often contain source data or generated files.
**/input/*
!**/input/README.md
**/output/*
!**/output/README.md
outputs/*
!outputs/README.md

# Large tabular/binary research artifacts should be shared separately unless sampled.
*.csv
*.tsv
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.xlsm
*.parquet
*.feather
*.pkl
*.pickle
*.h5

# Team/internal report artifacts require separate publication review.
제안서&운용보고서/**/*.pptx
제안서&운용보고서/**/*.pdf
제안서&운용보고서/**/*.docx

# Empty local scratch file.
전략_notebook/04_검색량데이터_전략/삼성전자_회귀베타계산
